skill.name: Fists of Thunder
skill.description:
Generate: 14 Spirit per attack

Teleport to your target and unleash a series of extremely fast punches that deal 200% weapon damage as Lightning.

Every third hit deals 400% weapon damage as Lightning split between all enemies in front of you.
skill.simpleDescription:
Generate: 14 Spirit per attack

Teleport to your target and attack it with a series of rapid punches.

rune.name: Thunderclap
rune.description: Release an electric shockwave with every punch that hits all enemies within 6 yards of your primary enemy for 120% weapon damage as Lightning and causes knockback with every third hit.
rune.simpleDescription: Release an electric shockwave with every punch and cause knockback every third hit.

skill.name: Mantra of Conviction
skill.description:
Cost: 50 Spirit

Active: Damage bonus is increased to 20% for 3 seconds.

Passive: Enemies within 30 yards of you take 10% increased damage.

Only one Mantra may be active at a time.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 50 Spirit

Active: Damage bonus is increased for a short duration.

Passive: Nearby enemies take increased damage.

Only one Mantra may be active at a time.

rune.name: Submission
rune.description: Passive: Enemies affected by Mantra of Conviction take 38% weapon damage per second as Holy.
rune.simpleDescription: Passive: Enemies affected by Mantra of Conviction take Holy damage over time.

skill.name: Dashing Strike
skill.description:
Cost: 1 Charge

Quickly dash up to 50 yards, striking enemies along the way for 370% weapon damage as Physical.

You gain a charge every 8 seconds and can have up to 2 charges stored at a time.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 1 Charge

Quickly dash and strike enemies.

You gain a charge every 8 seconds and can have up to 2 charges stored at a time.

rune.name: Barrage
rune.description: The last enemy you dash through is obliterated with a barrage of strikes, taking an additional 975% weapon damage as Physical over 2 seconds.
rune.simpleDescription: The last enemy you dash through is obliterated with a barrage of strikes.

skill.name: Sweeping Wind
skill.description:
Cost: 75 Spirit

Surround yourself in a vortex that continuously deals 105% weapon damage to all enemies within 10 yards. The vortex lasts 6 seconds and is refreshed each time you strike an enemy with a melee attack. Landing a Critical Hit has a chance to increase the vortex effect up to 3 stacks for a total of 315% weapon damage.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 75 Spirit

Surround yourself in a vortex for 6 seconds that damages nearby enemies. Critical Hits intensify the vortex.

rune.name: Blade Storm
rune.description: Intensify the vortex, increasing the damage per stack to 145% weapon damage. This increases the damage with 3 stacks to 435% weapon damage.
rune.simpleDescription: Increase the damage of Sweeping Wind.

skill.name: Seven-Sided Strike
skill.description:
Cost: 50 Spirit
Cooldown: 30 seconds

Dash rapidly between nearby enemies, dealing 5677% weapon damage over 7 strikes.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 50 Spirit
Cooldown: 30 seconds

Move with blinding speed and strike nearby enemies while being immune to attacks yourself.

rune.name: Sudden Assault
rune.description: Teleport to the enemy and increase damage dealt to 8285% weapon damage as Lightning over 7 strikes.
rune.simpleDescription:
Teleport to the enemy and increase the damage per strike.

Seven-Sided Strike's damage turns into Lightning.

skill.name: Mystic Ally
skill.description:
Cooldown: 30 seconds

Active: Your mystic ally has its damage increased by 50% for 10 seconds.

Passive: A mystic ally fights by your side. The ally deals 130% of your weapon damage as Physical per swing. When the ally dies, it is reborn after 5 seconds.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 30 seconds

Active: Your mystic ally has its damage increased for a short duration.

Passive: A mystic ally fights by your side.

rune.name: Fire Ally
rune.description:
Active: Your mystic ally splits into 10 allies that explode for 290% weapon damage as Fire.

Passive: A mystic ally fights by your side that increases your damage by 10%.
rune.simpleDescription:
Active: Your mystic ally splits into multiple allies that explode.

Passive: A mystic ally fights by your side that increases your damage.

skill.name: Chant of Resonance
skill.description: The Spirit costs of Mantra activation effects are reduced by 50% and you gain 4 Spirit every second when you have a Mantra learned.
skill.flavor: The world continues on the noble path, each of us carrying another, all connected, ever onward.

skill.name: Transcendence
skill.description:
Every point of Spirit spent heals you for 429 Life.

Heal amount is increased by 0.4% of your Health Globe Healing Bonus.
skill.flavor: A life unlived is no different from death.

skill.name: Combination Strike
skill.description: Each different Spirit Generator you use increases your damage by 10% for 3 seconds.
skill.flavor: Master Wughan was not merely the first to perfect the six techniques. His true accomplishment was in weaving them into a style all his own.

skill.name: Exalted Soul
skill.description:
Increase maximum Spirit by 50 and increase Spirit Regeneration by 4 per second.

Spirit fuels your defensive and offensive abilities.
skill.flavor: "Endeavor to be one with the hidden truth and you will soar beyond the sky." â€”Waykeeper Tzo Krin

skill.name: Heal
skill.description:
Cooldown: 30 seconds

Heals you and the Templar for 193112 Life.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 30 seconds

Heals you and the Templar.

skill.name: Intimidate
skill.description: Enemies that hit or are hit by the Templar are slowed by 80% for 3 seconds.
skill.simpleDescription: Enemies that hit or are hit by the Templar are slowed.

skill.name: Onslaught
skill.description:
Cooldown: 10 seconds

Delivers a massive blow to an enemy for 800% weapon damage.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 10 seconds

Delivers a massive blow to an enemy.

skill.name: Inspire
skill.description:
Increases your resource generation.

Mana: 7 per second.
Hatred: 1 per second.
Wrath: 1.1 per second.
Arcane Power: 1.4 per second.
Fury: 10% generated.
Spirit: 10% generated.

skill.name: Crippling Shot
skill.description:
Cooldown: 4 seconds

Ranged attack that deals 140% weapon damage and slows enemies hit by 80% for 4 seconds.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 4 seconds

Ranged attack that slows enemies.

skill.name: Dirty Fighting
skill.description:
Cooldown: 6 seconds

Blinds nearby enemies in front of the Scoundrel for 2 seconds.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 6 seconds

Blinds nearby enemies in front of the Scoundrel.

skill.name: Powered Shot
skill.description:
Cooldown: 8 seconds

Ranged attack that explodes on impact, dealing 310% weapon damage as Arcane to enemies within 10 yards and has a 100% chance to Stun enemies for 2 seconds.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 8 seconds

Deals damage in an area that has a chance to Stun enemies.

skill.name: Anatomy
skill.description: Increases Critical Hit Chance by 1.8% for you and the Scoundrel.
skill.simpleDescription: Increases Critical Hit Chance for you and the Scoundrel.

skill.name: Forceful Push
skill.description:
Cooldown: 5 seconds

Summon an Arcane explosion 8 yards around an enemy, dealing 410% weapon damage as Arcane and knocking back all monsters caught within it.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 5 seconds

Creates an explosion that deals massive damage and knocks back enemies.

skill.name: Powered Armor
skill.description: Buffs you and the Enchantress, increasing Armor by 3% and slowing melee attackers by 60% for 1 seconds.
skill.simpleDescription: Increases Armor and slows melee attackers for you and the Enchantress.

skill.name: Disorient
skill.description:
Cooldown: 6 seconds

Cast a flash of light in an area, causing enemies to be disoriented for 2 seconds.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 6 seconds

Disorients enemies for a short time.

skill.name: Mass Control
skill.description:
Cooldown: 18 seconds

Lob a bulb of magical energy that hexes enemies in an area into chickens for 5 seconds.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cooldown: 18 seconds

Hexes a nearby group of enemies.
